# Foreword

I am [Caleb Jin](https://www.sjin.name/). After I read this paper, **[Bayesian reduced rank regression in econometrics](https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/0304407695017739)**[@Geweke], I write down the nodes of the key idea and R code to realize it.
